flowchart LR
    Dev[Developer] -->|git push / PR| GH[GitHub Repository]
    GH -->|pre-commit locally| PC[Pre-commit hooks]
    GH -->|CI: lint + test + build + push| GHA[GitHub Actions]
    GHA -->|Docker image| DH[Docker Hub]
    GHA -->|update Helm values| Repo[(GitOps repo path)]
    Repo --> ARGO[ArgoCD]
    ARGO --> K8S[Kubernetes / EKS]
    K8S --> APP[TaskFlow App Pods]
    K8S --> PROM[Prometheus]
    K8S --> LOKI[Loki]
    PROM --> GRAF[Grafana]
    LOKI --> GRAF
    PROM --> ALERT[Alertmanager]
    ALERT -->|webhook| CHAT[Slack / Discord / Teams]
    APP -->|metrics /metrics| PROM
    APP -->|stdout logs| LOKI
    TF[Terraform] -->|provisions| K8S
    SECRETS[GitHub Secrets / K8s Secrets / AWS Secrets Manager] --> GHA
    SECRETS --> K8S
